He is indeed a good candidate.

299
00:15:14,159 --> 00:15:14,799
Yes.

300
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,879
But I want to observe him a bit more.

301
00:15:21,879 --> 00:15:22,840
Don't worry.

302
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,919
I can still handle it.

303
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,960
I won't die earlier than you.

304
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,039
Take care.

305
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:31,799
