00:17:06,336 --> 00:17:07,640
Have you ever thought about it?

319
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,279
Suppose...

320
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,039
I'm just supposing

321
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,359
that Heilun

322
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:17,079
