326
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:31,160
His son also has a bad temper

327
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,559
but he's not as capable as Heilun.

328
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,839
Anyway, he always makes trouble

329
00:17:39,359 --> 00:17:41,279
