330
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:51,000
Or would you prefer your leader

331
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:53,119
to be a trustworthy

332
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:56,000
and smart person?

333
00:17:57,279 --> 00:17:58,119
Boss.

334
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,200
Heilun...

335
00:18:00,319 --> 00:18:01,119
What happened?

336
00:18:02,214 --> 00:18:06,037
♪When the name is buried in dust♪

337
00:18:06,246 --> 00:18:09,553
♪There's still a heartbeat
